thread.title: Iveta Ivanova

author: Iveta Ivanova
title: Iveta Ivanova
text: No options to talk to anyone rather than the chat. The online options do NOT cover everything you may need and there are way too many charges for changes online. It should be all free, company doesn't care about customers and will do everything not to talk to you, pushing for online charged services. Not possible to reach out to anyone via phone, very disappointing.
